mysqlLogin()

Description
    bool mysqlLogin(string $username, string $password, object $engine)
    Checks a username and password in a mySQL database.  If the pair exists, sets $_SESSION['username'] to $username and $_SESSION['authType'] to "mysql".

Parameters
    username
	String value containing a username.

    password
	String value containing user's password.

    engine
	The engine object.

Return Values
    Returns boolean value, indicating success or failure.
